history.proof: intros l i H. induction l as [|e es IH]. - simpl. auto. - simpl. destruct (leb (eIndex e) i) eqn:Heindex. + apply sorted_cons. * sfirstorder depth: 3. * intros e' Hine. apply H in Hine. destruct Hine as [Heindex' Heterm]. split. ++ sfirstorder depth: 3. ++ apply Heterm. + apply IH. apply H.

exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet *: Current bullet * is not finished.
Wrong bullet ++: Current bullet ++ is not finished.

original: intros l i H. induction l as [|e es IH]. - simpl. auto. - simpl. destruct (leb (eIndex e) i) eqn:Heindex. + apply sorted_cons. * apply IH. apply H. * intros e' Hine. apply H in Hine. destruct Hine as [Heindex' Heterm]. split. ++ apply Nat.leb_gt. apply Heindex'. ++ apply Heterm. + apply IH. apply H.
